<span id="freeTextContainer11960042857659424780">From the author of the international bestseller <i>Incendiary</i> comes a haunting novel about the tenuous friendship that blooms between two disparate strangers—one an illegal Nigerian refugee, the other a recent widow from suburban London.</span>

