    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_93925269" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/93925269" />
    <a title="Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1237196-petra-is-like-a-jigsaw-fragmented-pieces-missing"><img alt="Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1642342196p2/1237196.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/93925269?book_show_action=true">Mar 13, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing" href="/user/show/1237196-petra-is-like-a-jigsaw-fragmented-pieces-missing">Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1237196-petra-is-like-a-jigsaw-fragmented-pieces-missing?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1237196-petra-is-like-a-jigsaw-fragmented-pieces-missing?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer93925269" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15992488810859740798">This is a book you should buy and not borrow from the library. Just to reward the author for such an amazing and exhilarating experience. Its as much like watching a film as it reading a book because the writing is so extraordinarily good (and clever). And this review is so dry because the author wants nothing of his book revealed. &quot;The magic is in the way the story unfolds,&quot; he&apos;s said, and yes, it is. <br/><br/>And I am <i>sooo </i>going to enjoy hand-selling people this book in my shop. I will have so many hap</span>
  <span id="freeText15992488810859740798" style="display:none">This is a book you should buy and not borrow from the library. Just to reward the author for such an amazing and exhilarating experience. Its as much like watching a film as it reading a book because the writing is so extraordinarily good (and clever). And this review is so dry because the author wants nothing of his book revealed. "The magic is in the way the story unfolds," he's said, and yes, it is. <br /><br />And I am <i>sooo </i>going to enjoy hand-selling people this book in my shop. I will have so many happy customers.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15992488810859740798" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


